    "text": "Police Creating Accountability by Making Effective Recording Available Act of 2021 or the Police CAMERA Act of 2021\n\nThis bill authorizes the Bureau of Justice Assistance within the Department of Justice to make grants for states, local governments, and Indian tribes to purchase or lease body-worn cameras for use by law enforcement officers and to implement body-worn camera programs."
